[## [SECTION: What You Will Build]]

1
01:05:00,000 --> 01:05:06,000
In Phase 3, we build the core retrieval infrastructure.
This is where text becomes vectors and vectors become searchable.

2
01:05:06,000 --> 01:05:12,000
You will learn how to use tiktoken for exact token counting.
How to build section-aware chunkers that respect document structure.

3
01:05:12,000 --> 01:05:18,000
How to generate embeddings using both OpenAI and local models.
And how to store and search those embeddings using pgvector.

4
01:05:18,000 --> 01:05:24,000
By the end of this phase, you'll have a fully functional vector search system.
You can ingest documents and find relevant passages by semantic meaning.



